  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |
    Snap ML Chess Hints
    
    This Lens demonstrates how to use the Snap ML pipeline on Spectacles together with the Remote Service Gateway (AI services).
    
    In this example, the user identifies a real chessboard and is guided to manually select two vertices of the chessboard plane facing them. After pinching the two positions to align the digital plane with the physical chessboard, the experience recognizes the board in space.
    
    Once the setup is complete, the user can tap the **“Hint”** button to receive real-time strategy suggestions based on the current state of the game.

